messageBody:
For my part I'm putting the blame for my absence firmly on Real Life.
My work was ambushed by a pack of rabid auditors, we got rid of them but
I'm still recovering. :(
I'll be back in a week or two, once I've found the will to live again.

Perhaps a good first step would be to setup a test wiki and see how that
goes?
